Citygate Global was founded in June 2007 as a Microfinance Institution and registered with Corporate Affairs Commission. The organisation was created with the objective to reduce Nigerian population living below poverty line by intervening and enhancing the capacities of the low-end actively engaged populace struggling to run a viable businesses to earn a living. The organisation activities are geared in line with the global initiative of poverty alleviation and Financial Inclusion to all. We continually focus on this segment of the Nigerian economy by doing everything possible to assist them to run a viable businesses and improve their lives.We are recruiting to fill the position below:Job Title: Direct Sales AgentLocation:&nbsp;Lagos&nbsp; Apply at https://ngcareers.com/job/2019-07/direct-sales-agent-at-citygate-global-investment-limited-794/ Source: NG Career Mosgbenks Global Services Limited (MGS) is a new Education consulting firm registered with Corporate Affairs Commission. We are recruiting to fill the position below: Job Title: Direct Sales Agent Location: Lagos Job Description Identifies business opportunities. Actively seeking out new sales opportunities through cold calling, networking and social media. Setting up… June 28, 2019 In "Jobs" Nurudeen Hamza The federal government is, for the umpteenth time, admitting that unemployment and underemployment are the greatest challenges of the Muhammadu Buhari administration. Briefing members of the National Economic Council (NEC) at the Presidential Villa recently, the Minister of Budget and National Planning, Senator Udoma Udo Udoma, identified lack… September 30, 2017 In "News" NWP Global is a global organisation created with the mission of Ending Poverty and Unemployment across the globe - with particular attention on AFRICA. Our strategy is to empower youth and women - with requisite skills and knowledge that will help secure high reward jobs and/or start their own successful… November 26, 2017 In "Jobs"